translated: Ericstam, Per Göte, dentist in Borås, born on January 20, 1911 in Ransäter, Värmland county, son of pastor Eric E. and Emerentia Aspenberg. Married in 1938 to Mary Helena Orstadius. Children: Jan-Åke (born in 1938), Per-Erik (born in 1942), Björn (born in 1945). He completed his secondary education in Borås in 1929, graduated from dental school in 1931, and became a licensed dentist in 1933. He worked as an assistant in Falkenberg from 1933 to 1934, and then started his own practice in Borås.
